{"tid":1392701,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1907號熱帶氣旋 韋帕 WIPHA（08W）＃3","createTime":"2019-07-31T23:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T00:25:51.000Z","uid":83172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82ef4d0a7f16bab24e5e28fc270ceefb6f71f06d","tid":1392701,"uid":83172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 </ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1907號熱帶氣旋 韋帕 WIPHA （08W）  </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：泰國<br />\n意義：婦女的名字</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　<br />\n為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　<br />\n請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　<br />\n <br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png&h=d512611e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png&h=7ef830e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png&h=54316817&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7sNQ3N2.png&h=15a63bfa&s={SIZE}\" /></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1910.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1910.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_1910.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1907-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1907-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/1907-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://pzal.ndbc.noaa.gov/collab/jtwc/products/wp0719.gif\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201908W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/WIPHA.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"},{"pid":"437eebf630d2eb094e79c2f71c2d90940830f880","tid":1392701,"uid":2617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"在過去一小時，長洲、橫瀾島及大老山分別錄得的最高持續風速為每小時87、77及68公里，最高陣風分別為每小時108、98及96公里。<br />\n<br />\n天文台又比人整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce4e2d30886ab9d34cc04d457909aec014824f2","tid":1392701,"uid":83172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392702\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392702</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用另一個post</span></span>"},{"pid":"523c2f2827d507e3bc2f864b77d23953192614f8","tid":1392701,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"437eebf630d2eb094e79c2f71c2d90940830f880","tid":1392701,"uid":2617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"在過去一小時，長洲、橫瀾島及大老山分別錄得的最高持續風速為每小時87、77及68公里，最高陣風分別為每小時108、98及96公里。<br />\n<br />\n天文台又比人整蠱<img src=\"/assets/fac